ab850a6754b5"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Instructions to install the Mongo Community Edition (Windows, Mac, Linux) \
that can be found in ",
 ButtonBox["MongoDB Install",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/administration/install-community/"], 
    None},
  ButtonNote->
   "https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/administration/install-community/"],
 "."
}], "Subitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775564567522856*^9, 3.7755646501979523`*^9}, {
  3.7764270311554*^9, 3.776427046015328*^9}, {3.776428115858118*^9, 
  3.77642812781383*^9}, {3.776444226845004*^9, 3.776444227692178*^9}, {
  3.776492158100122*^9, 3.776492160466849*^9}, {3.779961169306015*^9, 
  3.779961177262062*^9}, {3.7799612348990726`*^9, 3.7799612757835484`*^9}, {
  3.813513755115763*^9, 3.8135138245613813`*^9}, {3.813513857100258*^9, 
  3.813513872862693*^9}, {3.813513972452886*^9, 3.813513979751768*^9}, {
  3.813656403272541*^9, 
  3.813656403278593*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1513ebf6-1006-4f23-a907-\
30edc880b230"],

Cell["\<\
For Windows. I would recommend that you DO NOT click the box to install the \
Wizard Mongo DB Compass, which is a wizard to query data from the database, \
but it is not the data base management system Mongo DB. After installing \
Mongo DB, you should find it in the application folder, and then you go to :\
\[NonBreakingSpace]
C:\\Program\[NonBreakingSpace]Files\\MongoDB\\Server\\4.4\\bin\\
The executable file is there, just click in MongoDB
You should then see the screen for the MongoDB server.
If you want to install the Wizard Mongo DB Compass, you will find the \
installer in the same folder as where you find Mongo.  \
\>", "Subitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775564567522856*^9, 3.7755646501979523`*^9}, {
  3.7764270311554*^9, 3.776427046015328*^9}, {3.776428115858118*^9, 
  3.77642812781383*^9}, {3.776444226845004*^9, 3.776444227692178*^9}, {
  3.776492158100122*^9, 3.776492160466849*^9}, {3.779961169306015*^9, 
  3.779961177262062*^9}, {3.7799612348990726`*^9, 3.7799612757835484`*^9}, {
  3.813513755115763*^9, 3.8135138245613813`*^9}, {3.813513857100258*^9, 
  3.813513872862693*^9}, {3.813513972452886*^9, 3.813513979751768*^9}, {
  3.813656404230165*^9, 3.813656503665965*^9}, {3.813656545756944*^9, 
  3.813656556267787*^9}, {3.907224455770041*^9, 
  3.907224456016702*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"182f529b-49ea-488c-bfee-\
bf457f8f27d4"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "For Mac, you will need to install Homebrew. OSX does not include the \
Homebrew brew package by default. Install brew using the ",
 ButtonBox["official instructions",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://brew.sh/#install"], None},
  ButtonNote->"https://brew.sh/#install"],
 "."
}], "Subitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775564567522856*^9, 3.7755646501979523`*^9}, {
  3.7764270311554*^9, 3.776427046015328*^9}, {3.776428115858118*^9, 
