67c765674372"],

Cell["\<\
To stop a MongoDB running as a macOS service, use the following command as \
needed :\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.813514265501787*^9, 3.813514265504775*^9}, 
   3.813514316022531*^9, {3.813525501219499*^9, 
